<div id="contact">
	<div class="transition"></div>
	<div class="container center marginTop">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<%= simple_form_for @contact_form do |f| %>
				<%= f.input :name, required: true, label: "Your Name" %>
				<%= f.input :email  %>
				<%= f.input :message, required: true, as: :text %>
				<%= f.button :submit, "Send" %>
				<% end %>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<h1>Thank you for visiting!</h1>
				<p>This visual journal of photos and videos that I've shot professionally and for enjoyment over the years displays some of the beauty that I've discovered in my affiliations and explorations. I've lived in a few amazing cities and have had a wide range of jobs and freelance positions over the years.</p>
				<p>If you're interested in booking me for your next project, please fill out this form for any pricing quotes and inquiries.</p>
				<h2>I look forward to collaborating with you!</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="marginTopMin"></div>
</div>